modDescription:
Huge underground [vault](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-prefab/) located in the empty wasteland city in Navezgane. Its a long journey and danger lurks in the dark! (Go at night with no flashlight for the full experience!).

I tried to make this a difficult one, so come prepared!

There is a deadly climb to escape!

A shovel and splints are recommended!

The Navezgane world folder just includes the prefab.xml to save space! Make a copy of your Navezgane world and replace the prefab.xml!

More install info in the readme!

I wish you luck survivor!

**[Download](https://github.com/NoSadFaces/7D2D_UndergroundVault_POI/archive/master.zip)**

**Credits:** Kelsey
